PrecisRe-appointment of PETER LUSZTIG, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a British Columbia Treaty Commissioner, as nominated by Canada, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of two years, effective April 14, 1997 and ending on the earlier of April 13, 1999, or the date on which the appointment is terminated.
